The paper focuses on developing a new approach to learn graph-level representations using recurrent neural networks. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
